pos_mean_info_list.mean: 昂贵地；仔细地；过分讲究地

word_mean_info__list.difference: 指有相当价值，可高价出售的，或有用、有益的东西。
指因稀罕、不易得到而很值钱，或因本身的品质而具有极大的价值。

bilingual.source: Of all possessions a friend is the most precious.
bilingual.target: 在所有财产中，朋友是最珍贵的。
金子是一种非常珍贵的金属。

bilingual.source: A ruby is a very precious gemstone.
bilingual.target: 红宝石是一种非常珍贵的宝石。
时间是我们最珍贵的资源。

bilingual.source: Time is precious, so use it wisely.
bilingual.target: 时间是珍贵的，所以要明智地利用它。
我们不能丢失这些珍贵的照片。
他收藏了一块珍贵的端砚。
羊肚菌是一种非常珍贵的食材。

bilingual.source: The taj was encrusted with precious gems.
bilingual.target: 这顶王冠镶嵌着珍贵的宝石。
她收藏了许多珍贵的纪念品。

list.abstract: precious（英 [ˈpreʃəs]，美 [ˈpreʃəs]），英语单词，作形容词为贵重的；珍贵的；故作风雅的等。作名词为宝贝；亲爱的。In college, time is scarce, and consequently, very precious.（在大学里，时间是稀缺的，因此是非常宝贵的。） precious的近义词有golden；valued。
《Precious》是张杰演唱的歌曲，Written by为Jason Zhang、Venus Brown、T Coles、Riley Urick，收录于《Precious》专辑中，于2018年2月5日发行。

yingyinNormal.en: Uncle's most precious, born in the Year of the Monkey. That's why you're so clever, precious and clever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 舅舅最珍贵的小宝贝，猴年出生，所以你才如此聪慧，珍贵且聪慧。

yingyinNormal.en: All the bright, precious things fade so fast. And they don't come back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 华美珍贵的事物总是很快逝去，而且一去不复返。

yingyinNormal.en: The theater is a temple of art. A precious cornucopia of creative energy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 剧场是艺术的殿堂，剧场能孕育出珍贵的创造力。

yingyinNormal.en: Pass me a napkin. Is milady's arm broken? Yours is about to be. Aww, precious flowers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 递我一张纸巾吧。夫人的胳膊断了吗？你的胳膊就要被我打断了。祖国珍贵的花朵。

yingyinNormal.en: To fight back, plants began to evolve a whole arsenal of defences for their precious leaves.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为了反击植物进化出一系列的武器来保卫它们珍贵的叶子。

yingyinNormal.en: Those test subjects, those turtles, running in their blood is the last of this precious mutagen.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些实验对象，那些乌龟，他们血液里流淌着的就是这种珍贵的突变体。

yingyinNormal.en: All right. What is in the safe? Something for you. Maurice always said it was his most precious gift to you. A will. Maurice's will is with Port and Dunn.
yingyinNormal.zh: 箱内有什么东西？是给你的，令尊说过 那是给你最珍贵的礼物，一份遗嘱。他的遗嘱在律师那里。

yingyinNormal.en: To have a precious few of them back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 宝贵的时光一去不复返啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, Precious. Mike's not worth this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听着，珍贵，麦克不值得你这样。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh please. Every moment is precious. You know?
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜托，每分每秒都很珍贵。

yingyinNormal.en: And my precious souvenir snow globe collection.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有我全球的雪景水晶球。

yingyinNormal.en: You are so precious, I could just take you home.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瞧你可爱的，真想带你回家。

yingyinNormal.en: Only 8,000? We're wasting precious time. Buy it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只有八千把？我们在浪费宝贵时间，快买下。

yingyinNormal.en: It is precious to you beyond measure, I understand that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在你眼中是无价之宝我，能够理解。

yingyinNormal.en: Time is the single most precious commodity in the universe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为只有时间在宇宙中才是最为宝贵的资源。

yingyinNormal.en: Why waste precious time dreaming when waking life is so much better?
yingyinNormal.zh: 既然醒时的生活如此美好，为何要把宝贵时间浪费在做梦上呢？

yingyinNormal.en: That is precious. Listen, I need Rachel's flight information. Oh, okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可爱死了！！！听着，我要瑞秋的航班信息，哦，好。

yingyinNormal.en: All right. Susie. Can I call you Susie? My name is Precious. I can't say that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好的，苏希，我能叫你苏希吗？我的名字叫珍贵。我叫不出口。

yingyinNormal.en: You can't have your precious memory falling into the wrong hands, now, can you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不能让自己的宝贵记忆被敌人窃取，是吗？

yingyinNormal.en: A precious few people know about your true identity. It would be unfortunate if we forgot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没什么人知道你的真实身份，要是我们不小心忘了就惨了。

examination_example.sentence: To pressure zoos to spend less on their animals would lead to inhumane outcomes for the <highlight>precious</highlight> creatures in their care.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 迫使动物园减少在动物身上的花费会对园内的珍贵动物造成不人道的后果。

word_usage.usage:
precious和valuable都可以表示“贵重的”，区别在于：
precious指无法用钱衡量的珍贵的东西，尤其适用于失去后无法补偿的东西，还可用于人的感情；
valuable指值钱的、可以带来巨额利润的，或有用的、有益的东西。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 侧重于事物本务的贵重，precious也侧重于人或事物在某人看来是可贵的。
主要指值钱的，其次指有用的、有帮助的、有意义的。
